### 1. Register New User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@watsons.co.th",
  "password": "password123",
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User",
  "phone": "086-111-2222",
  "role": "END_USER"
}

### 2. Login (ใช้ user จาก seed data)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@rim.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 3. Login (ใช้ user ที่เพิ่งสร้าง)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@watsons.co.th",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 4. Get Current User (ต้อง login ก่อน แล้วเอา accessToken มาใส่)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 5. Test Invalid Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@rim.com",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

